name: 17th International Conference on Osteoporosis, Arthritis and Musculoskeletal Disorders
content: Osteoporosis 2022 takes immense pleasure in welcoming all the participants from across the globe to attend the “17th International Conference on Osteoporosis Arthritis and Musculoskeletal Disorders” during January 23-25, 2023 in Dubai, UAE. The conference comprises eminent personalities with their keynote presentations, verbal speeches, productive poster presentations, and exhibitions along with a discussion forum providing insights on Osteoporosis.
